Le Lac dor (The Golden Lake) is a 25 acre venue surrounded by
woodland and nestled in the French countryside. This mature lake is
an ideal holiday venue with three log cabins each with their own
pegs accommodating up to 4 anglers for you to fish from. The
size of the fish that reside here is the most impressive feature
with some huge specimens lurking beneath the surface waiting to be
caught
